    "description": "Standoff Beat is a fast-paced rhythm-based fighting game that combines the concept of rock-paper-scissors with the adrenaline of a 1v1 duel. On every beat, you must make a choice : shoot, reload, dodge, or cast a special ability unique to your fighter. Timing and decision-making are crucial as each beat brings you closer to victory—or defeat.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChoose from a diverse roster of fighters, each with their unique stats, passive abilities, and a powerful special move. The game features multiple stages, each with its atmosphere and soundtrack that controls the rhythm of the fight.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhether you're training against CPU opponents or squaring off against friends in intense multiplayer matches, Standoff Beat offers endless replayability. Pick your fighter, sharpen your reflexes, and master their abilities,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAre you ready to face the music and win the standoff?",
